Privacy Policy for Weight Tracker

Effective Date: 03/12/2023

Thank you for using Weight Tracker! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application and related services (collectively, the "App").

1. Information We Collect
1.1 Information You Provide

We may collect information that you voluntarily provide when using the App, such as:

Account information: When you create an account, we may collect your name, email address, and other relevant details.
User-generated content: We may collect information, including text, images, and other content, that you submit through the App.
1.2 Automatically Collected Information

We may automatically collect certain information when you use the App, including:

Device information: We may collect information about your device, such as the device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.
Usage information: We may collect information about how you use the App, including the pages you view, your interactions with features, and other usage patterns.
2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including:

Providing and improving the App's functionality.
Personalizing your experience within the App.
Communicating with you, such as responding to your inquiries or providing updates.
3. Information Sharing
We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:

With your consent.
For legal reasons, such as to comply with applicable laws or respond to legal requests.
4. Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information we collect from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.

5. Your Choices
You may have the ability to control certain information we collect through your device settings or preferences. Additionally, you can contact us to update or request the deletion of your information.

6. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at bertayyonel@gmail.com.
